			"description": "**FCIN**\n\n- Retrieve\n    \n- Delete\n    \n\nNote.\n\nCreate and Update operations are not allowed.\nFCIN is automatically created when parent FCNT (with fcied=true) is updated.\nAccess latest via /la, oldest via /ol (same as CIN).\nRequires RVI=4."
